805
00:37:10,124 --> 00:37:11,541
[Sobs]

806
00:37:11,625 --> 00:37:13,459
There's no living
with it.

807
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:16,012
No matter what
we decide.

808
00:37:16,096 --> 00:37:18,965
[Running footsteps]

809
00:37:24,521 --> 00:37:28,391
[Blowing breaths]

810
00:37:35,282 --> 00:37:38,701
