what was going on.

814
00:37:44,325 --> 00:37:46,359
She's pinking up.

815
00:37:46,410 --> 00:37:48,361
She must have yanked off
her ivs and oxygen.

816
00:37:48,412 --> 00:37:50,897
Came here to die.

817
00:37:59,910 --> 00:38:01,878
<i>(Taub)</i>
<i>By unhooking herself</i>
<i>from everything,</i>

818
00:38:01,929 --> 00:38:04,614
<i>she delivered a hypoxic</i>
<i>insult to her body</i>

819
00:38:04,682 --> 00:38:07,751
<i>that started</i>
<i>a downward spiral.</i>

820
00:38:07,802 --> 00:38:09,436
<i>(Foreman)</i>
<i>If you're gonna make</i>
<i>a decision,</i>

821
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:11,305
<i>you're running out of time.</i>

822
00:38:20,064 --> 00:38:22,115
Hr can't find you
a new supervisor.

823
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:23,600
How come?

824
00:38:23,668 --> 00:38:26,203
Because you're
unsupervisable, House.

825
00:38:26,270 --> 00:38:27,954
Two department chairs
threatened to quit.

826
00:38:28,022 --> 00:38:30,407
Well, I guess
we're stuck with each other.

827
00:38:33,211 --> 00:38:36,279
I have no idea why
I'm making this call

828
00:38:36,331 --> 00:38:38,448
or if it's
the right call to make.

829
00:38:38,516 --> 00:38:40,217
But if you feel strongly

830
00:38:40,284 --> 00:38:43,787
about presenting the parents
your treatment option,

831
00:38:43,838 --> 00:38:46,790
you can do it.

832
00:38:46,841 --> 00:38:49,309
Thank you, I will.

833
00:38:49,394 --> 00:38:51,595
Several hours ago.

834
00:38:51,662 --> 00:38:53,847
You told them?

835
00:38:53,915 --> 00:38:56,650
I told him.
He came to my office.

836
00:39:00,555 --> 00:39:03,423
I'm sorry.

837
00:39:06,010 --> 00:39:09,780
Well...I should probably
be more mad at you.

838
00:39:11,416 --> 00:39:12,916
Yeah.

839
00:39:14,752 --> 00:39:17,287
Dr. House?

840
00:39:17,338 --> 00:39:19,056
