As much as they may
wanna pass the lung here!

853
00:39:47,235 --> 00:39:48,852
Of course they do!

854
00:39:48,903 --> 00:39:50,654
You're handing them
an impossible choice.

855
00:39:50,705 --> 00:39:52,906
Life has handed them
a crappy choice,

856
00:39:52,990 --> 00:39:54,708
