between decade and year?

861
00:40:03,134 --> 00:40:04,468
Their son
is a human being.

862
00:40:04,535 --> 00:40:05,919
You know what they are,
right?

863
00:40:06,003 --> 00:40:08,588
Intrinsic value.
We don't get to decide--

864
00:40:08,673 --> 00:40:10,674
and we do it every day.
If the two of them needed

865
00:40:10,725 --> 00:40:12,759
the same lung--
he needs to keep the one he's got.

866
00:40:12,844 --> 00:40:15,395
You don't get to play God
by ripping out--

867
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:17,864
that train left the station when
we learned to do transplants.

868
00:40:17,932 --> 00:40:19,599
The rest is just
paper-pushing.

869
00:40:19,684 --> 00:40:21,902
Of course, now we're on to your
